Source: German Legal References Benchmark (10k)
Split: validation (to avoid test-set leakage)
Selected: 15 plain-text + 5 HTML + 5 Markdown documents for CI fixture subset
Selection criteria: court diversity (BGH, BVerfG, BVerwG, BAG, BSG, BFH, OLG, LG, VG, LAG, BPatG),
  document length mix (short <2000, long >10000 chars), preference for docs
  with both law and case citations.
